---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import FAQSchema from "../../../components/FAQSchema.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Carpet Cleaning Saint-Lambert | Luxury Residential Service"
  description="Expert carpet and upholstery cleaning in Saint-Lambert. Ultra-powerful truck-mount service for impeccable results and fast drying. Local trusted company."
>
  <div class="split-hero-container">
    <div class="container full-width-split">
      <div class="split-layout">
        <div class="split-content fade-in-section">
          <span class="service-cat-badge">LOCAL EXCELLENCE • SAINT-LAMBERT</span>
          <h1 class="split-title fade-in-up text-gradient-empire">
            Carpet & Sofa Cleaning in Saint-Lambert
          </h1>

          <div class="problem-statement fade-in-up delay-100" style="border-left-color: var(--color-accent);">
            <h3 class="problem-title" style="color: var(--color-primary);">A Standard of Quality:</h3>
            <p class="problem-text">
              For Saint-Lambert residents, home maintenance is a priority. Between heritage estates and prestige apartments, your carpets and furniture deserve treatment that preserves their value and aesthetics.
            </p>
          </div>

          <p class="lead-text fade-in-up delay-200">
            Empire Cleaning Group provides Saint-Lambert citizens with a deep steam extraction cleaning solution. Using our truck-mount technology, we eliminate the toughest stains and allergens while guaranteeing ultra-fast drying times.
          </p>

          <div class="cta-group fade-in-up delay-300">
            <a href="tel:5148939939" class="btn btn-gradient-green pulse-btn">
              <span class="icon">📞</span> (514) 893-9939 (Saint-Lambert Service)
            </a>
            <button onclick="window.openEstimationWidget()" class="btn btn-gradient-green">
              <span class="icon">⚡</span> Free Online Quote
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="split-image-wrapper fade-in-section delay-200">
          <div class="slideshow-container">
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/camion-usine-nettoyage-empire.webp"
              alt="Our steam extraction truck-mount parked in Saint-Lambert"
              class="slide active"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              fetchpriority="high"
              loading="eager"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/team-nettoyage-empire.webp"
              alt="The Empire Cleaning Group expert team ready for Saint-Lambert"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/resultat-nettoyage-escaliers-tapis.webp"
              alt="Impeccable result after carpet stair cleaning in Saint-Lambert"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="image-overlay-gradient"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-layout">
        <div class="service-main">
          <div class="fade-in-section delay-100">
            <h2 class="section-title text-gradient-empire">
              Why Trust Us in Saint-Lambert?
            </h2>
            <p>
              We know that Saint-Lambert residents look for more than just a cleaning service: they look for peace of mind.
            </p>
            <ul class="benefit-list" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
              <li>
                <strong>Industrial Suction Power:</strong> Unlike portable machines, our truck-mount vacuums dirt and water directly into our exterior tanks, leaving your carpets nearly dry immediately.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Specialized Stain Removal:</strong> Red wine, coffee, or pet accidents? Our technicians use specific solutions for each fiber type to dissolve stains without damaging fabrics.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Delicate Textile Care:</strong> We are experts in cleaning velvet, cotton, and linen sofas, as well as maintaining fine wool rugs.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Eco-Friendly Commitment:</strong> We use biodegradable products that are safe for your family and pets, while being ruthless against dirt.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Professional & Courteous Service:</strong> Our technicians arrive on time, protect your hardwood floors, and leave your home spotless.
              </li>
            </ul>

            <div style="margin-top: 3rem; background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px;">
              <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                🏙️ Service Tailored to the Saint-Lambert Lifestyle
              </h3>
              <p>
                Whether it's a modern condo near the station or a historic home on Riverside Drive, we have the equipment and expertise to adapt to all housing configurations, ensuring a discreet and efficient service.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-main" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
          <div class="zones-section" style="margin-top: 3rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
            <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.4rem;">We Serve All of Saint-Lambert:</h3>
            <div class="city-group">
              <div class="badges-container">
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Victoria Sector</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Riverside Drive and surroundings</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Near Victoria Bridge</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Préville</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="contact-footer">Expert cleaning in Saint-Lambert: <strong>(514) 893-9939</strong>.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="fade-in-section delay-300" style="margin-top: 3rem;">
            <h2 class="section-title text-gradient-empire">
              Cleaning FAQ — Saint-Lambert
            </h2>
            <FAQSchema
              faqs={[
                {
                  question: "Can your truck-mount park on Saint-Lambert's narrow streets?",
                  answer: "Yes, absolutely. Our hoses extend over 200 feet, allowing us to remain safely parked on the street or driveway while reaching all rooms in your home.",
                },
                {
                  question: "How long must I wait before walking on my cleaned carpet?",
                  answer: "Thanks to our powerful extraction, the carpet will be dry to the touch within a few hours (3 to 6h). We recommend waiting until the next day for complete deep drying.",
                },
                {
                  question: "Are your products safe for apartments with limited ventilation?",
                  answer: "Absolutely. Our solutions are free of toxic fumes and biodegradable. Furthermore, our steam extraction process does not add excessive humidity to your apartment's air.",
                }
              ]}
            />
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<script>
  const slides = document.querySelectorAll(".slide");
  if (slides.length > 0) {
    let currentSlide = 0;
    setInterval(() => {
      slides[currentSlide].classList.remove("active");
      currentSlide = (currentSlide + 1) % slides.length;
      slides[currentSlide].classList.add("active");
    }, 4000);
  }
</script>

<style>
  .split-hero-container { background-color: #fff; padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; overflow: hidden; width: 100vw; }
  .full-width-split { width: 100%; max-width: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .split-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0; align-items: stretch; min-height: 80vh; }
  .split-content { background-color: #ffffff; padding: 100px 4rem 4rem 10%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
  .service-cat-badge { text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 0.85rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .split-title { font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 3.5vw, 4rem); color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.1; }
  .city-group { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .badges-container { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .badge { padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem; border: 1px solid transparent; }
  .badge-blue { background: #e8f4fd; border-color: #c5dff0; }
  .problem-statement { background: #ffffff; border-left: 4px solid #ff4444; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0; margin-bottom: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(174, 206, 235, 0.3); }
  .problem-title { font-size: 1rem; color: #cc0000; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; }
  .problem-text { font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--color-text-main); font-style: italic; }
  .lead-text { font-size: 1.15rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--color-text-main); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; max-width: 650px; }
  .cta-group { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .cta-group { display: none !important; } }
  .split-image-wrapper { position: relative; height: 100%; min-height: 500px; width: 100%; }
  .slideshow-container { position: relative; width: 100%; height: 100%; overflow: hidden; }
  .slideshow-container img.slide {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100% !important;
    height: 100% !important;
    object-fit: cover !important;
    object-position: center !important;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 1.5s ease-in-out;
  }
  .slideshow-container img.slide.active { opacity: 1; }
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .split-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; min-height: auto; }
    .split-content { padding: 3rem 1.5rem; order: 1; }
    .split-image-wrapper { order: 2; height: 400px; min-height: 0; }
  }
  .service-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 5rem; }
  .section-title { font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; display: inline-block; }
  .benefit-list { margin: 2rem 0; list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .benefit-list li { margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; position: relative; font-size: 1.05rem; }
  .benefit-list li::before { content: "✓"; color: #d32f2f; position: absolute; left: 0; font-weight: bold; }
  .contact-footer { margin-top: 1.5rem; font-style: italic; color: #666; }
</style>
